overview:
Manning Search Marketing was established in 2004 as a search engine marketing company based in Canada specializing in Organic SEO, Social Media Optimization, Local SEO, PPC and website design that is run by Gerard Manning, who has been working as a Search Marketing Specialist since 2000. Manning Search Marketing specializes in managed search engine optimization/marketing services for small to medium sized businesses.

Our fundamental goal is to fulfill clients with providing them with an unsurpassed search engine marketing campaign from the ground up to properly deliver the results needed for their company/business to succeed in todayâ€™s ever changing online marketing world.

We deliver high quality search marketing services, from in-depth keyword research to ensure proper keywords are targeted, technical/organic website audits making sure all aspects of the website are up to par, website optimization, online/offline optimization, link building, and SEO consulting services.
